# remove-cast-str-to-text

## Description

Migrated from the hand-coded `cast_optimization_rules` to a declarative `.rra` rule
(RFC 0090). The rewrite is expressed as structured data below.

## Rewrite

lhs: (cast (const-str ?val) text)
rhs: (const-str ?val)
